---Component Diagram----

Actor; User 
Components: Mobile OR Web client , UniRide Backend API , user management as Auth, ride management, booking managment, 
notfication Component, database as DB , Map API / geolocation

Client--> backend : REST API ( api/auth , api/rides, api/bookings, api/notifications)
Backend --> Auth
Backend --> RideMgmt
Backend --> BookingMgt
Backend --> Notif

Auth --> DB : users
RideMgmt --> DB: rides, vehicles 
BookingMgmt --> DB: bookings 
Notif --> DB: notifications

RideMgmt --> MapAPI: getRout(), getcode()
BookingMgmt --> Notif: bookingcreatesd, booking Approved 
RideMgmt --> Notif: rideCancelled 
